<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Arnold von Seckendorff, Hofmeister [Markgraf Friedrichs I. von Brandenburg,] und Kaspar von Buttendorf, Vogt zu Gunzenhausen</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Geleit für Nürnberger Bürger und Kaufleute auf dem Weg zu und von der Nördlinger Messe.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_125" id="61v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_125_r1l14"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Arnolt<ex>en</ex></expan> von Sekendorff <expan>Hofmeıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_125_r1l16"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>H<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>Hofmeıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> wır <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mıt fleıſſ / Daʒ Jr <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_125_r1l17"><expan>beſtell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wellet daʒ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> vnd kawffleẅt vnd auch Jr hab vnd kawff </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_125_r1l18"><expan>manſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> vnd dıe Jren <expan>yecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan> ın <expan>Nördlıng<ex>er</ex></expan> markt vnd <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> darauſʒ durch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_125_r1l19"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>Marggr<ex>afen</ex></expan> <expan>frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von <expan>Brandemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> / vnd <expan>Burggr<ex>afen</ex></expan> ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_125_r1l20"><expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>rſchaft</expan> vnd gepıete <expan>ſıch<ex>er</ex></expan> geleytet <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> wenn ſıe <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıe Jren </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_125_r1l21"><expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd des <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> / Als etc / Das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc / Vnd lat vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_125_r1l22"><expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> eẅr <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> antwurt <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> bey dıſem <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> dıener </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_125_r1l23"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter"><ab facs="#facs_125_r1l24">
<add>Caſpar von pütendorff</add> vogt ʒu Guncʒenhawſen <expan>ſı<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_125" id="61v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Arnolt<ex>en</ex></expan> von Sekendorff,
                            <expan>hofmeist<ex>er</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>hofmeist<ex>er</ex></expan>, wir <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr
                                <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit fleiss, daz ir
                                <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>bestell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wellet, daz
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und kawfflewt und auch ir hab und
                                kawff<expan>mansch<ex>aft</ex></expan> und die iren
                                <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> in
                            <expan>Nördling<ex>er</ex></expan> markt und
                            <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> darausz durch
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>marggr<ex>afen</ex></expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von <expan>Brandemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> und
                                <expan>burggr<ex>afen</ex></expan> zu
                            <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>, <expan>h<ex>e</ex>rschaft</expan> und
                        gepiete <expan>sich<ex>er</ex></expan> geleytet
                            <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, wenn sie <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        die iren <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> und des
                            <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>. Als etc. Das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        etc. Und lat uns <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ewr
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> antwurt
                            <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> bey disem <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
                        diener. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab><add>Caspar von Pütendorff</add>, vogt zu Gunczenhawsen
                                <expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>.</ab>
</div>
